eutron cloud surrounds the clusters during\nthe early stages of the expansion, resulting in systems that give rise to\nconfigurations compatibles with the emergence of r-proccess. Conclusions: These\ncalculations pave the way to a comparision between Earth experiments and\nneutron star studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 18:13:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
