ds for mission critical parts) for AM in\nthis emergent stage so that mitigations can be applied before accidents occur.\nA second purpose of this white paper is to evaluate the effectiveness of STPA\nas a hazard analysis technique in a field that is still relatively new.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 20:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-05"}
